Mollie King shot to fame as one fifth of girlband The Saturdays but the singer, who is known and loved for her forward-forward style, has been quietly carving out a successful career for herself in fashion. 

With two successful sell-out edits already under her belt, the 27-year-old is once again collaborating with Oasis to launch her Loved By Mollie edit - a carefully selected pick of her favourite pieces from the high-street store.

Mollie has selected 15 pieces she believes encapsulate the season’s key trends, which she models to perfection in the new campaign imagery.

