Speaking to FEMAIL at the exclusive unveiling of the new range at Balthazar restaurant, the stylish star said: 'I'm so excited to be back again working with Oasis because I had so much fun the first two times around and the reception was fantastic. 

'What I love about Oasis  as a high street store is that it's really trend-led but also affordable.'

The latest edit is a selection of key wardrobe staples, including classic stripes and khaki accents, which Mollie says are perfect for taking you from day to night. 

