'As a brand we are delighted to be working with Mollie for her ultimate edit of key picks for SS15. With the brilliant reaction to her previous two edits we’re sure our customers will love this one too.’

Mollie's fashion career is going from strength to strength after she was snapped up by Next Model Management and is now a regular fixture on the most starry fashion week front rows  and parties.

